c89238f3dcb5ed4125f47a330e7e4660 (02:47): Just a disclaimer. I will disconnect immediately if you:
a) say 'asl'/equivalent
b) say 'm or f'/equivalent
c) use this smiley: XD
N.B. i WILL be able to tell if you're an nooby teenager (I regret my use of the word 'noob'). I will be able to tell if you're an ASL-er in disguise. I will be able to tell if you're any breed of pseudo-non-noob, so don't even try.
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:48): i had no intention of any of that
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:48): but what if i mixed it up and asked las
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:49): i mean im not really asking las
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:49): but you specifically said "asl" was off limits
c89238f3dcb5ed4125f47a330e7e4660 (02:49): youre on dodgy grrounds here
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:49): im thinking you should be more specific. people are gonna be asking you las
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:50): im just trying to help you with your disclaimer
c89238f3dcb5ed4125f47a330e7e4660 (02:50): then they fulfill the pseudo-noob category
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:50): but could be better, you know?
c89238f3dcb5ed4125f47a330e7e4660 (02:50): and i cut them off asap
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:50): didnt read the fine print
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:50): yeah now that i look closer
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:51): so, if i may ask, what are you trying to accomplish by getting so specific with your disclaimer? i mean, it was up there immediately
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:51): so does it work pretty well for you
c89238f3dcb5ed4125f47a330e7e4660 (02:52): no point in beating around the bush to be honesyt
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:52): you findin some real quality friends and shit?
c89238f3dcb5ed4125f47a330e7e4660 (02:52): it's nice when others are on the same wavelength
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:52): when you just said cheers, i thought you were about to leave
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:52): i guess i always thought it was meant as a "Goodbye"
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:53): my understanding of cheers is an old sitcom with kirstie alley's nasty ass
c89238f3dcb5ed4125f47a330e7e4660 (02:53): i can tell youre a yank
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:54): im not sneakily trying to get to "asl"
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:54): it was a conversational question
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:54): oh nice, i talked to someone from london yesterday
b31cd51981b2ea6c8b26633ddc41d31e (02:55): thanks, wanna do some crack with me later? sniff it off of my ass?
